    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> tschneidereit created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13840#discussion_r3545554528\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Done — the thread-local now initializes straight from the <code>fetch_add</code>, no sentinel or <code>Cell</code> needed.</p>\n</blockquote>",
