        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"memo\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4dd\" role=\"img\" title=\"memo\">:memo:</span> tschneidereit submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13840#pullrequestreview-4655978216\">PR review</a>.</p>",
