    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13840#discussion_r3546049537\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ah ok, it make sense that it helps a bit but I feel like I keep reading various bits and pieces on the internet about how doing this is a bad idea. I think the bad idea part though specifically stems from taking up way too much space for frequently allocated things, which this doesn't fall under, so seems fine to leave</p>\n</blockquote>",
